 Former Big Brother Naija ‘Shine Ya Eye’ Housemate, Maria Chike Benjamin has sought the help of a native doctor popularly called bone setter as her knee injury worsens. The reality TV star cum actress recently suffered an injury that left her with a broken knee. Taking to her Instagram page, Maria shared a video of herself being treated by a local doctor as she cries out in pain.  Maria, who seemed to have been receiving treatment from an undisclosed hospital, said the doctor was wrong as the knee injury was getting worse. She wrote: “I’ve never cried so badly in my life, He straightened my broken knee. The doctor was wrong cause it was getting worse. So I got a local medicine man. And he put the bone back in. I wouldn’t wish the pain on my worst enemy. So more bed rest”